Text: While using this application, I've found that it's MUCH better than 1st printed. It also includes a full-version Reg Scan/Clean, and Derangementer, as well as an excellent Start-up Application User Interface which tells you what each Application does, where it's from, and it's RISK etc. I highly recommend this App be used by every (PFFT) Windows system, and for the size, you should at least take a look at it.
